1. Write ChangeLog entry.

2. make dist, check that it builds and installs correctly.

3. Commit (git status, git add all modified files, git commit).

4. Tag as Release_X_Y_Z (git tag -a -s Release_X_Y_Z).

5. Make new tarball, sign (gpg -b) and upload dist tarball 
   (sftp larsl@dl.sv.nongnu.org:/releases/ll-plugins).

6. Update webpages (including changelog).

7. Announce on http://freshmeat.net and any relevant mailing lists.
